Build instructions:

1) Install IzPack from the jar (java -jar IzPack-install-4.3.1.jar)
2) set IZPACK_HOME to your IzPack installation (eg: export IZPACK_HOME=~/IzPack/)
3) make sure 'ant' is on your $PATH
4) make sure 'mvn' is on your $PATH
5) Update any of the files in the distribution directory that may need updating. Careful, some of them contain variables that will be parsed by IzPack.
6) update 'appversion' tag in ergo_install.xml
7) Execute the build script (./build_installer.sh)
